metadata.name: Mad Mouse
metadata.description: 5555 Mad Mouse Circus NFTs native to the Ethereum blockchain. Each newly created NFT begins at Level 1 and is assigned one of the following roles: Clown, Juggler, Magician, Trainer, or Performer. Mad Mouse Circus NFT holders will be able to take part in the levelling system to evolve their NFTs from Level 1 to Level 3.
